  "introduced_at": "2007-10-18",
  "number": "3908",
  "official_title": "To direct the Architect of the Capitol to ensure that the Pledge of Allegiance to the Flag and the national motto \"In God We Trust\" are each displayed prominently in the Capitol Visitor Center on a permanent basis and to prohibit the Architect from removing or refusing to include language or other content from exhibits and materials relating to the Capitol Visitor Center on the grounds that the language or content includes a religious reference or Judeo-Christian content.",
